Package: triwise
Title: Gene expression changes in three biological conditions.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Wouter", "Saelens", email = "wouter.saelens@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The triwise package provides function to analyze and visualize gene expression in three biological conditions. Gene expression is converted to a barycentric representation allowing the representation of each gene in a 2D plane.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
